title: NoSleep Podcast S14E14
description:
It’s Episode 14 of Season 14. This week we conjure spells for you about the oh so innocent things which will shatter us. “Tainted” written by W.C. Jones (Story starts around 00:05:45) Produced by: Jeff Clement Cast: Jessica – Jessica McEvoy, John – Elie Hirschman, Old woman – Erin Lillis, Old woman’s son – David Cummings, Submarine Man – Jesse Cornett, Nurse – Nichole Goodnight “Spider” written by Joseph Yenkavitch (Story starts around 00:39:40) Produced by: Phil Michalski
